Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:58.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:02.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}轻微地颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:16.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:41.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:46.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:50.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:02.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:06.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:10.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:15.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:37.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:44.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:47.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:50.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:55.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:59.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:05.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:10.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:16.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:21.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:27.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:32.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:38.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:43.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:48.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:51.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:55.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都会从你的影子中看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是您经常光顾的花店商
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝醉之后买了大量的花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能帮我处理掉一些的话 会很感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家没花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您专程打电话来问我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么挑的时间这么巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在附近的深山里有人目击了像是斯卡的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的目的地 恐怕就是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废矿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这巴兹库尔现在已经成了幽灵都市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好作为藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以分开找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各部队 找到斯卡后马上联系我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与艾尔利克兄弟同行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是来监视我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}巴兹库尔的激斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么才能甩掉他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才看到人影了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是进了那边的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡和那孩子在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 如果对方不主动出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想找可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真的见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道阿尔大人是追着我来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想详细问下炼丹术的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办 是不是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔大人和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（喂 小丫头）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想见你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不会再让你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把你的炼丹术教给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟围着我强夺爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦 爱德华大人不是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 撞到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人 那女人是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过份 阿尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 她只是青梅竹马的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 为什么我非要像个脚踏两条船的男人一样找藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅 不要一个人跑那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 我 马可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那脸 怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你们为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别说你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是尤斯威尔伟大的碳矿主尤基大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了 应该说我不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明做了那么过份的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（1914年）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（尤斯威尔）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碳矿之镇 尤斯威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尤基曾是统治那里的军人兼碳矿经营者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏我的统治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇上的人幸福地生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（滞纳的税金）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（快点给我交上来）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（是因为你拖欠工钱才交不出的！）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然出现了绝世恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（银怀表！？）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（国家炼金术师！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（金块！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（这些用来买你的碳矿权利书）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那却是个巧妙的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（这是怎么回事 炼金术师大人！？）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（从你那里得到的金块全部变成了石头！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他们背后串通好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我被骗走了碳矿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被忘恩负义的城镇居民欺负得很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被军部冠上莫须有的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了再起 在各地展开事业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为依靠的投资也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向大富豪请求善意的融资
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我发誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我要复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们使我落到这步田地的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要对他们施行比死亡更可怕的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会输给你这种狐狸精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我说…狐狸精是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 我们之间真的没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 快点说炼丹术的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很艰辛吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要敷衍我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到温莉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你们在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从查理队抽两个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 是斯卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果找到他的话 也会马上通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是斯卡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利大人久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子真灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就两个人能把我怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人的话 办不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是普通人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合成兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后知道了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 是贤者之石的制作法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是这个国家的成立
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为了追求清国炼丹术的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追着这孩子来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 很早就有人察觉到这一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那个人留下的研究书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们觉得这本书里应该有解决的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 如果能解读那本书的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也许有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那需要斯卡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么需要那家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是斯卡所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是军队的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉和马可先生藏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿尔去看看状况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么胖 动作却很快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不接触身体就无法破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我们从这个距离慢慢消磨你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不妙的话就破坏落脚点这点习惯也研究透了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你打得遍体鳞伤后再交给金普利大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来得还真凑巧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙是中央都市派遣来的金普利随从
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就乖乖站在那里看着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡现在由我们捉拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 下流胚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干…干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不认识这种非人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装作自己人想要吃我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面的胖子嘴巴也好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会被囫囵吞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小鬼 乖乖待着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 好像比斯卡速度还快？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好轻 好轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手脚就像羽毛一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美妙 寒地专用机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 居然小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拳头也变轻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的唾液可没那么简单就消除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是口水吗 真脏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我这招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唾液的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分解的话 基本上就是水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干了什么？哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮肤要被扒下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用湿的手接触冷的金属就会结冰的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妨碍我们 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我们这边的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不认识你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且怎么看那角色都是敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说是我们的同伴就拿出证据来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我现在解除变身 你好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等这个时候好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞帕诺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在敌人面前收起武器 真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 稍微睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就乖乖让我们抓住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去应该去的地方接受惩罚 斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍我的家伙都要排除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然什么都不想笔直地冲过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那钢之右臂 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 这已经不是钢的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 为什么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请退下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做些不得了的研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑在那边的柱子上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制裁同族虽然很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能放过你这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说同族？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就由我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 别接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想好好面对面地谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么杀了我的父母？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论说什么听起来都像是辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了洛克贝尔医生夫妇这件事是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是联络中提到的大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过了约定的24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位女王大人 真的会封锁出口的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是灭掉灯 摸索着前进的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们一直强调说点灯的话怪物就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把他们送去医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说过经过24小时就把洞封上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:19:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 还没到24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提 这怀表是阿姆斯壮少将给的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先遣队没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算带回两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的冬天真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有黑和白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常分明 我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬头看的话 也有蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人的心情是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回多谢您怜悯我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么
