Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员退下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 为什么没好好看着温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利先生 在房顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是伴随悲伤的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但邂逅本身就有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往复的感情标记着前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
